The X Factor Australia - Season 5, Episode 1




The X Factor is back with amazing new talent and a fresh and fun new judging panel. Ronan Keating and Natalie Bassingthwaighte return as judges, but this year are joined by Dannii Minogue and LMFAO's Redfoo. They've travelled the country to find Australia's best new talent and tonight will see who has The X Factor.



Original Air Date: 29-Jul-2013
